
==============
Apache kafka
==============

=> Kafka is used as a message broker (mediator between applications).

=> Kafka is used as distributed streaming platform.

=> Kafka is used for real-time data processing.

=> Kafka helps to send data from one application to another application asynchronsouly.

=> Kafka extremely fast, scalable, and reliable.

=> Kafka Can process millions of messages per second.

=> Kafka software is free and open source, developed by Apache org.


=> Kafka works based on pub-sub model.

		publisher : The application which stores msgs in kafka

		subscriber : The application which reads msgs from kafka


===============
Kafka usecases
===============			

1) swiggy & zomoto orders processing

2) ola, uber and rapido cabs booking

3) Flights journey data processing


===================
Kafka Architecture
===================

1) Zookeeper (Provides runtime to run kafka server)

2) Kafka Server (Message Broker)

3) Kafka Topic (Message queue , to store msgs)

4) Publisher Application (The appliation which sends msgs to kafka topic)

5) Subscriber Application (The application which recieves msgs from kafka topic)


